casebody.data:
Thebaud et al. v. Great Western Ins. Co. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. May 24, 1889.) Appeal from circuit court, New York county.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Bartlett, JJ.

P. M. Butler, for appellant. Ha/rrington Putnam, for respondents. Van Brunt, P. J.

Judgment reversed, and new trial ordered, with costs to the appellant to abide event, on opinion in Thebaud v. Insurance Co., ante, 619.
